frameDefinitions: Words in this frame have to do with a Cognizer creating a new intellectual entity, the Idea.
The Authorities put a Prisoner in Prison as punishment for an Offense.
An Agent wants to achieve a Goal,  or an object.
A Cognizer introduces a New_idea into society.
This frame has to do with nouns denoting types of entities.
An Agent performs a series of unspecified tasks to plan for an Event to take place at a Scheduled_time and Place.
frameExamples: I 've been trying to <t>come up</t> with a plan .
US Drug Researcher <t>Imprisoned</t> for FDA Fraud.
The modest American <t>goal</t> of a threefold increase in capacity recognises this fact .
It is difficult to imagine how different our lives would be without Edison's <t>invention</t> of the light bulb.
I don't like this newfangled <t><fex name='Subtype'>kind</fex></t> of  fish.
I've <t>arranged</t> a breakfast meeting for you tomorrow morning with Mr. Huntsberger.
listRoleDefinitions:
Cognizer is the person who comes up with or conceptualizes the Invention. It is normally expressed as an External Argument: 

<fex name='Cognizer'>Kim</fex> <t>devised</t> a new recipe.
Invention is the intellectual creation of the Cognizer. It is normally expressed as an NP Object, but sometimes as a PP Complement:
The <fen>Time</fen> when the <fen>Idea</fen> is created.
The location in which the <fen>Cognizer</fen> comes up with the <fen>Idea</fen>.
The person who is confined in a penal institution.
The <fen>Prison</fen>  within which the <fen>Prisoner</fen> comes to be confined.
The <fen>Authorities</fen> are the institution or actors carrying out the imprisonment.
The time when the imprisonment happens.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the <fen>Prisoner</fen> is kept.
The volitional actor who intends to achieve a goal.
The action or state of affairs that the Agent wants to achieve.
A <fen>Means</fen> is an object or action that is used or designed to achieve a particular <fen>Goal</fen>.
This role marks expressions that indicate an <fen>Attribute</fen> for which it is the <fen>Agent</fen>'s goal that it have or reach a particular <fen>Value</fen> .
This role marks expressions that indicate which <fen>Value</fen> the <fen>Agent</fen> wants the <fen>Attribute</fen> to reach.
This Frame Element expresses a time period during which an <fen>Agent</fen> had a particular <fen>Goal</fen>.
The <fen>Cognizer</fen> comes up with or conceptualizes the <fen>New_idea</fen>. It is normally expressed as an External Argument:
The <fen>New_idea</fen> is a concept not previously present in society which the <fen>Cognizer</fen> introduces.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the <fen>Cognizer</fen> comes up with the <fen>New_idea</fen>.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the <fen>Cognizer</fen> comes up with the <fen>New_idea</fen>.
The entity which denotes a subtype of the more general <fen>Category</fen>.
The more general type that the target denotes a subtype of. This role is obligatory and should be labeled DNI when not present.
The person who makes arrangements for the <fen>Event</fen> to take place at a <fen>Time</fen> and <fen>Place</fen>.
The incident for which the <fen>Agent</fen> has made arrangements.
The time for which the <fen>Agent</fen> has arranged the <fen>Event</fen>.
This role describes the time at which the arrangements are made.
The location at which the <fen>Agent</fen> has made arrangements for the <fen>Event</fen> to take place.
listRoleExamples: Kim devised <fex>a new recipe</fex>.
You had better hatch some plans <fex>before you get there</fex>.
She had cooked up the story <fex>in Pisa</fex>, before she even left Italy.
<fex>Man</fex> Falsely Imprisoned for 24 Years Seeks Damages
When she returned, <fex>the Chaoyang Town government authorities</fex> imprisoned her for 5 days.
<fex>Microsoft 's</fex> goal of delivering a million copies in the first year is trifling compared to the 25 million copies of Windows it has shipped since May 1990.
The company missed its goal <fex>of getting a thousand third-party software packages shipped</fex>.
The goal <fex>of treatment</fex> was to lower diastolic blood pressure below 85 mm  Hg .
We exceeded our <fex>production</fex> target of 2000 units
GM has a production target <fex>of 2,000,000 units</fex>
But the main goal <fex>of the 1990s</fex> could be to transform a big , heavily armed standing army into a more flexible force
<fex>Kim Sung</fex> invented cinnamon cheez fries in 1988.
The strong gravitic shield was discovered <fex>in 2162</fex>.
Was the light bulb invented <fex>in Austria</fex>?
I don't like this <fex>kind</fex> of fish.
They created a new breed <fex>of dog</fex>.
<fex>Lucy</fex> organized a playdate for little Michael and Marcy.
I've already made <fex>vacation</fex> arrangements.
I've put together a luncheon <fex>for 12:30</fex>.
Lionel organized a meeting <fex>at the local pub</fex> to discuss the bleak future of our organization.
